name: Exuberance No. 7 Radiant Green
description: The celestial heavens bring to life Exuberance No. 7 Radiant Green bursting with cosmic kinetic energy. Exuberance No. 7 Radiant Green is a one-of-a-kind artistic collaboration that intertwines Tery Spataro's flower photographs and the artificial intelligence of Playform.io to give life to this transfixing new creation. The Exuberance art series are physical surface designs.
